---
title: Spicy Salsa Verde Turkey Tacos with Crema & Pico de Gallo
description: You know what time it is—it’s taco time! So, let’s get with the program: To start these spicy tacos, ground turkey is first seasoned with our smoky Mexican spice blend then sizzled with zesty green salsa for a flavorful filling. You’ll spoon it over steamy tortillas and top with quick homemade pico de gallo and cooling crema. A bright squeeze of fresh lemon juice completes this hearty handheld meal.
